"""
        Test that a TypeError is raised when an invalid value is used to set
        the profile name of a ProfileInformation structure.
        """
kwargs = {'profile_name': 'invalid'}
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'The profile name must be a ProfileName enumeration.', objects.
    ProfileInformation, **kwargs)
args = objects.ProfileInformation(), 'profile_name', 'invalid'
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'The profile name must be a ProfileName enumeration.', setattr, *args)
